          "annotations": [
            {
              "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3b27qh58/canvas/p3/annopage",
              "type": "AnnotationPage",
              "items": [
                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3b27qh58/manifest/annotation/p3",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>municated all this to you? If he has, did he give you also the<lb/> name of “A Jew.”?\n                At all events, I will give it to you. It is<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr. <hi rend=\"underline\">Charles H. Moise</hi></persName>. I do not envy\n                him for the laurels which<lb/> he has won in this warfare; all he gained is this,\n                that the Press of <placeName>S. C.</placeName><lb/> become lukewarm &amp;\n                indifferent, after some papers had taken<lb/> up our cause. Nevertheless, a memorial\n                will be sent to the President<lb/> by Jews, if not <hi rend=\"underline\">the</hi>\n                Jews of <placeName>Charleston</placeName>; it is now being circulated<lb/> for\n                subscription. Will you expose this extraordinary proceeding of a<lb/> Jew in this\n                affair? Justice demands it!</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I read your Article on the New Prayer-book “<hi rend=\"underline\"\n                    >Minhag</hi><lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\"><placeName>America</placeName></hi>,” in the last month's <hi\n                    rend=\"underline\">Occidents</hi>. I agree fully with you<lb/> concerning the\n                transgression of power by the Compilers; I wrote<lb/> the <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                    >same</hi> truths to <persName>Dr Cohn</persName> in\n                    <placeName>Albany</placeName>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">already two months</hi><lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">ago</hi>, that is, before you published your strictures. I\n                think the<lb/> very title is a piece of presumption and usurpation which<lb/> cannot\n                be justified save by means of vulgar abuse and<lb/> contemptible insults.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Now an open and honest explanation; I received your<lb/> invitation\n                to the Consecration of your Synagogue. I did not<lb/> answer, nor attend. Why?\n                Because I endorse every word contained<lb/> in the Editorial of the <hi\n                    rend=\"underline\">Asmonean</hi>, of <date>May 9.</date> last, and referring<lb/>\n                to the establishment of your congregation.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">With my wife's and my own best regard, and our wishes<lb/> for the\n                coming New-Year, I remain, as ever,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Yours,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">most respectfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Dr M Mayer</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>P.S. What is <persName>Mr. S. Jacobs</persName> doing? Is it </p>\n            <p>true, that he has been appointed Professor of </p>\n            <p>the Hebrew, at the Girard College, with a salary</p>\n            <p>of $2000 a year? So <persName>Mr A. H. Abrahams</persName> tells the people here.</p>\n            <p>What is is salary as Lecturer? Did you ever <sic>here</sic> the particulars of his\n                resignation?</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3b27qh58/canvas/p3"
                }
